<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <h2>Manage Clients</h2>
        <p>
            You can add new clients, and add new cases to existing clients. You can also see or edit 
            your clients information, edit or delete the clients. You can leave notes regarding the cases.
        </p>
        @*<p><a class="btn btn-default" href="https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=301865">Learn more &raquo;</a></p>*@
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <h2>Manage Cases</h2>
        <p>You can see and edit info about your cases. You can update status of your cases. Please remember that if you want to create a new case,
           go to 'Manage Clients' to create a client first, then add a new case. You can add a new case to 
           existing clients in 'Manage Clients'.</p>
        @*<p><a class="btn btn-default" href="https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=301866">Learn more &raquo;</a></p>*@
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <h2>Edit Status Selection</h2>
        <p>You can add edit or delete status selection menu so each time there is any change in the status, 
        you don't have to type in. You can just choose from a dropdown menu.</p>
        @*<p><a class="btn btn-default" href="https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=301867">Learn more &raquo;</a></p>*@
    </div>
</div>